* Create a Volume
** Required privileges
***_ CREATE VOLUME on the schema
***_ USE SCHEMA and USE CATALOG
***_ For external: CREATE EXTERNAL VOLUME
** Managed volume (SQL)
***_ CREATE VOLUME IF NOT EXISTS catalog.schema.volume
** External volume (SQL)
***_ CREATE EXTERNAL VOLUME ... LOCATION '...'
** Using Catalog Explorer
***_ Navigate to schema > Create > Volume
***_ Choose Managed or External type
** Inherits permissions from parent schema
@endmindmap
